name: Spider-Bae
description:
Spider-Bae's friends have been trapped by some mysterious force that won't be elaborated on because this game doesn't really have a story!

Swing through the four levels and save them as fast as you can! Or just chill out and swing around aimlessly because that's also pretty fun!

This is a fangame! Hakos Baelz, Hololive, etc © Cover Corp!
